# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in — NEVER commit the real key.
# The generative layer calls the models VIA OPENROUTER (decision Bea 2026-07-03; the
# key already exists as a GitHub secret and packages/ai uses the same pattern).
# The harness reads OPENROUTER_API_KEY from the environment (openai SDK with
# base_url=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1). Only the OPTIONAL [generativa] extra uses it;
# the offline CI and the substrate/search paths do NOT.
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
